        <value>
            <description>Having embraced anarchy since the very beginning, the slums of Randy are the defiant cities formed out of the chaos of the old House of Randy. The hardy citizens have adapted to a life clouded by smog, and a brain distracted by hard drugs.</description>
        </value>
    </Operation>
